  [ 20] getparam 1 .............................. <params>
  [ 22] getobjprop 2059 ......................... <params.attachDuration>
  [ 25] pusharglist 2 ........................... <[0, params.attachDuration]>
  [ 27] pushlist ................................ <[0, params.attachDuration]>
