end

on attachObjAttacked me
  [  0] getprop 2061 ............................ <pAttachObj>
  [  3] pusharglist 1 ........................... <pAttachObj>
  [  5] objcall 1722 ............................ <pAttachObj.getCharacter()>
  [  8] setlocal 0 .............................. objChar = pAttachObj.getCharacter()
  [ 10] getlocal 0 .............................. <objChar>
  [ 12] peek 0 .................................. case objChar of
  [ 14] pushsymb 2062 ........................... <#hair>
  [ 17] eq
  [ 18] jmpifz [ 29] ............................ (case) #hair:
  [ 21] getprop 2061 ............................ <pAttachObj>
  [ 24] pusharglistnoret 1 ...................... <pAttachObj>
  [ 26] objcall 1778 ............................ pAttachObj.cutOff()
  [ 29] pop 1
  [ 31] ret
end

on attachTo me, attachObj
  [  0] getparam 1 .............................. <attachObj>
